{"tid":2014849,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"華裔教授瞞報與華關係被捕","createTime":"2020-05-13T09:23:04.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-13T11:26:40.000Z","uid":25558,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"d62b81ff3b3c556ed0895a28d36668b9c392bf8e","tid":2014849,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-13T09:23:04.000Z","msg":"全文<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/20200513/RWN37TMBI7HVADSV7IUGMVED7A/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200513%2FRWN37TMBI7HVADSV7IUGMVED7A%2F&d=RJ6DAKdT%2BAkj0rfdhPz9NRx3ZeYPbPBc9Z3MXbd07rU%3D&h=6652357c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200513%2FRWN37TMBI7HVADSV7IUGMVED7A%2F&h=06753745\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/20200513/RWN37TMBI7HVADSV7IUGMVED7A/</a><br />\n<br />\n華裔教授瞞報與華關係被捕<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20200513/large/1589299782_db70.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20200513%2Flarge%2F1589299782_db70.jpg&h=dcda6d4c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n洪思忠<br />\n<br />\n美國阿肯色大學華裔電子工程學教授洪思忠（Simon Ang）上周五涉申請聯邦政府學術研究經費時隱瞞與中國政府有連繫被捕，司法部前日以「電訊詐騙」罪名起訴他，最高可判監20年，為華府打擊中國滲入美國學術界的另一行動。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：暗示彭斯正隔離 靠電話溝通<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n獲NASA資助3,900萬<br />\n<br />\n63歲的洪思忠為阿肯色大學高密度電子中心主任，該中心由國防部資助成立，相信曾為國際太空站提供技術。法庭文件指，洪思忠過去七年取得美國太空總署（NASA）等機構逾500萬。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n洪思忠瞞報與中國的關係被揭發，是因為大學一名圖書管理員在一個硬盤發現他去年6月曾向西安電子科技大學一名擬前。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n取美國的科技和貿易機密，並警告招聘海外專才參與頂尖研究項目的學府較易成為入侵目標，當局去年起已拘捕了多名「千人計劃」成員。<br />\n<br />\n美國《紐約時報》"},{"pid":"0b0f8b40d1db9cb69c4508a1f74dd157d84555f3","tid":2014849,"uid":302471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-13T09:30:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"899a5fbc98e6cea12c34e762da48395a051b2f07","tid":2014849,"uid":52090,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-13T11:09:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ae5ef2e178513435730d17003f4e964e90857aa","tid":2014849,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-13T11:12:46.000Z","msg":"偷咁多料火箭發射都係失敗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f468bd96dcc93573225d2467dbbb80b76bbb7cf","tid":2014849,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-13T11:15:54.000Z","msg":"老千人計劃?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90ba21ffe35f49305f9c27dc74617d8fd0d8350f","tid":2014849,"uid":19126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-13T11:18:32.000Z","msg":"63歲坐20年都係83姐，我地局長話你仲有成40年命玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ca725e565ef64d944fefe633e8f97860723b126","tid":2014849,"uid":20867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"90ba21ffe35f49305f9c27dc74617d8fd0d8350f","tid":2014849,"uid":19126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-13T11:18:32.000Z","msg":"63歲坐20年都係83姐，我地局長話你仲有成40年命玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-13T11:22:51.000Z","msg":"洪思宗(63)<br />\n黃碧雲(61)"},{"pid":"12274d6270d2acc220c3df9ad9ee011face7152a","tid":2014849,"uid":36901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-13T11:25:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://66.media.tumblr.com/32fad36d3731952382e40dff7d35a323/tumblr_pf8gvuOihz1u03abq_500.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F66.media.t